    "start": 6273.532,
    "end": 6305.196,
    "text": "outdoor for all ages and abilities grow appreciation and stewardship for our natural resources. I often find myself as hearings such as this speaking in support of policies and actions which put people's needs at the center of decision-making to ensure liveable, sustainable, and green communities. Thank you for allowing me the time to do just that tonight. next is phil witasa, following is jon russell."
