    "text": "incurring a needless penalty of more than 3 million dollars, no small matter that. From where I stand the council has all it needs to help the next logical step of development. That we are still debating this measure again so many months later suggests to me all of the good reasons in the world are not reaching the real reasons for debate and delay. My fear is that the real reason some on the council and some in"
