    "text": "used to explore and look for and play in the woods, we like the fresh air filtered by the mature forest. We had a barrier between us and stafford park and fairfax boulevard with all of the trees. We're now having problems with road ents and have seen foxes, raptors, and raccoon coming close to buildings since there's nowhere else for them to live. The surrounding neighborhoods are fine with bike lanes going"
