    "text": "and why still talking about it. Fairfax is a wonderful place to live, but the bureaucracy has the city has a stand still, move forward. Too many reject out of hand to move the city forward or support others than themselves. Remain that the city remain stagnant, that is not realistic or sustainable or what fairfax city is about. Fairfax city should be a place of inclusion and plan and that"
