    "text": "trail, 2024. I was like a trail, no biggie. And next I know stuck around for quite a while and a lot of interested parties. And granted where I grew up in germany, for example, we have trails everywhere and not a shocker. Hawai'I a lot of natural trails and you don't see as extensive or as large. So it's been interesting perspective to listen to the community, hear your feedback"
